        p.mb-0.font-weight-bold #seo #leads #organic #traffic #audience #target

section.info#info-4
  .container
    .row.align-items-center
      .col-12.col-md-6
        +infoPicture("wallpaper_autumn_branches", "Best practices")
      .col-12.col-md-6
        h3.my-4.mt-md-0.text-center.text-md-left Best practices
        p.mb-3.font-weight-bold.
          We follow the best practices for modern web development.
        p.mb-4.
          Web design is one of the most powerful digital mediums out there. Because of the huge role it plays,
          it is expected to undergo more shifts in technology than any other platform.
          The design also impacts your conversions, credibility, and ultimately makes or breaks the success of your site.
        p.mb-0.font-weight-bold #modern #web #development #good #practice #success

section.info#info-5
  .container
    .row.align-items-center
      .col-12.col-md-6.order-md-1
        +infoPicture("clouds_daylight_forest", "Accessibility")
      .col-12.col-md-6
        h3.my-4.mt-md-0.text-center.text-md-left Accessibility
        p.mb-3.font-weight-bold.
          Provide equal access, no barriers that prevent interaction.
        p.mb-4.
          Web accessibility is the inclusive practice of ensuring there are no barriers that prevent interaction
          with, or access to, websites on the World Wide Web by people with physical disabilities, situational
          disabilities, and socio-economic restrictions on bandwidth and speed.
        p.mb-0.font-weight-bold #equal #access #opportunity #people #disabilities #accessible

